= Burnley ([+ burnley_total_display +]% Approval)

The old industrial heart of the city that has since then went into quite some decline.

{!<b>!}Unemployed:{!</b>!} {!<b>!}[+ unemployed_burnley_approval_display +]%{!</b>!} supports Bruce. 
This is {!<b>!}[+ unemployed_burnley_support_display +]%{!</b>!} out of {!<b>!}[+ unemployed_burnley +]%{!</b>!} of the district population.
